# DataInput_New rules
# 1) Track Annotations fully (no ignore here)
# 2) Audio: ignore all file contents but keep the location folders via marker files
DataInput_New/*/Audio/**
!DataInput_New/*/Audio/**/.gitignore
!DataInput_New/*/Audio/**/.gitkeep
# 3) Processed: don't track anything
DataInput_New/*/Processed/**
# 4) Metadata: don't track anything
DataInput_New/*/Metadata/**
# Combined (generated aggregates) should not be tracked
DataInput_New/Combined/**

# 5 & 6) Diagnostics: track only top-level .py files; ignore subfolders and other files
Diagnostics/*
!Diagnostics/*.py

# 7) Results and other generated artifacts
TestResults/**
Assignations/**